Two-in-one beauty ritual for both your scalp and your skin.
Here’s how I use it:
	1.	Scalp Care – I run it gently through my hair to relax, stimulate blood flow, and help balance excess oil. It instantly calms my mind and feels sooo soothing.
	2.	Facial Gua Sha – The smooth side is perfect for a quick gua sha moment! It helps detox, de-puff, and gives my skin a natural glow.

Benefits I’ve noticed:
	•	Less scalp oiliness
	•	A fresher, more relaxed feeling after long days
	•	Reduced puffiness around my face (especially in the mornings!)

If you’re into holistic, multi-purpose beauty tools, you need to try this.
